 R‚ÜêTEST_CONSTELLATIONS;CDATA;SC;I;C;NAME;LINES;NSTARS;NTOTAL;ALLNAMES;J;S1;S2;XBOUND
‚çù Validate constellation stick figure connectivity data
‚çù Checks structure, index bounds, no self-loops, constellation membership
 R‚Üê1
 NSTARS‚Üê‚äÉ‚ç¥STARS
 CDATA‚ÜêCONSTELLATIONS
 SC‚ÜêSTARCONSTELLATION

‚çù --- STARCONSTELLATION must have 332 entries ---
 :If 332‚âÝ‚â¢SC
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: STARCONSTELLATION count expected 332, got ',‚çï‚â¢SC
   R‚Üê0 ‚ãÑ :Return
 :EndIf

‚çù --- CONSTELLATIONS must be non-empty ---
 :If 0=‚â¢CDATA
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: CONSTELLATIONS is empty'
   R‚Üê0 ‚ãÑ :Return
 :EndIf

‚çù --- Each element: (name lines) where lines is N√ó2 matrix ---
 :For I :In ‚ç≥‚â¢CDATA
   C‚ÜêI‚äÉCDATA
   :If 2‚âÝ‚â¢C
     ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: element ',(‚çïI),' is not a 2-element pair'
     R‚Üê0 ‚ãÑ :Return
   :EndIf
   NAME LINES‚ÜêC

‚çù Name must be a non-empty character vector
   :If 0=‚â¢NAME
     ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: element ',(‚çïI),' has empty name'
     R‚Üê0 ‚ãÑ :Return
   :EndIf

‚çù Lines must be a matrix with 2 columns
   :If 2‚âÝ‚ç¥‚ç¥LINES
     ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: ',NAME,' lines is not a matrix'
     R‚Üê0 ‚ãÑ :Return
   :EndIf
   :If 2‚âÝ(‚ç¥LINES)[2]
     ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: ',NAME,' lines matrix does not have 2 columns'
     R‚Üê0 ‚ãÑ :Return
   :EndIf

‚çù All indices must be integers in range 1..NSTARS
   :If ‚à®/(,LINES)‚âÝ‚åä,LINES
     ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: ',NAME,' has non-integer index'
     R‚Üê0 ‚ãÑ :Return
   :EndIf
   :If ‚à®/(,LINES)<1
     ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: ',NAME,' has index < 1'
     R‚Üê0 ‚ãÑ :Return
   :EndIf
   :If ‚à®/(,LINES)>NSTARS
     ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: ',NAME,' has index > ',(‚çïNSTARS)
     R‚Üê0 ‚ãÑ :Return
   :EndIf

‚çù No self-loops
   :If ‚à®/LINES[;1]=LINES[;2]
     ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: ',NAME,' has self-loop'
     R‚Üê0 ‚ãÑ :Return
   :EndIf

‚çù Every star must belong to the named constellation UNLESS it is a
‚çù documented cross-boundary link. These arise because:
‚çù   - Argo Navis (Car/Vel/Pup) was one constellation until 1763
‚çù   - Elnath (bTau 286) is traditionally shared by Auriga and Taurus
‚çù   - Alpheratz (1) forms a corner of the Great Square of Pegasus
‚çù   - Serpens Caput/Cauda straddle Ophiuchus
‚çù   - Stars 244 (gPer/gPhe) and 205 (dLyr/th1Ser) have wrong Bayer
‚çù     designations in the book ‚Äî their positions and HR numbers are
‚çù     correct, but STARCONSTELLATION reflects the wrong label.
‚çù Allowed: (constellation_name star_index) pairs
 XBOUND‚Üê‚ç¨
 XBOUND,‚Üê‚äÇ('Aur' 286)  ‚çù bTau/Elnath in Auriga pentagon
 XBOUND,‚Üê‚äÇ('Car' 322)  ‚çù gVel/Al Suhail ‚Äî Argo Navis
 XBOUND,‚Üê‚äÇ('Car' 323)  ‚çù dVel ‚Äî Argo Navis
 XBOUND,‚Üê‚äÇ('Peg' 1)    ‚çù aAnd/Alpheratz ‚Äî Great Square
 XBOUND,‚Üê‚äÇ('Phe' 244)  ‚çù book labels gPer, actually gPhe (Dec ¬Ø43)
 XBOUND,‚Üê‚äÇ('Pup' 322)  ‚çù gVel/Al Suhail ‚Äî Argo Navis
 XBOUND,‚Üê‚äÇ('Pup' 40)   ‚çù aCAR/Canopus ‚Äî Argo Navis
 XBOUND,‚Üê‚äÇ('Ser' 213)  ‚çù etOph/Sabik ‚Äî Serpens straddles Oph
 XBOUND,‚Üê‚äÇ('Ser' 216)  ‚çù nuOph ‚Äî Serpens straddles Oph
 XBOUND,‚Üê‚äÇ('Ser' 205)  ‚çù book labels dLyr, actually th1Ser (HR 7141)
   :For J :In ‚ç≥‚äÉ‚ç¥LINES
     S1‚ÜêLINES[J;1] ‚ãÑ S2‚ÜêLINES[J;2]
     :If (NAME‚â¢S1‚äÉSC)‚àß~(‚äÇNAME S1)‚àäXBOUND
       ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: ',NAME,' line ',(‚çïJ),' star ',(‚çïS1),' (',(S1‚äÉSTARNAMES),') belongs to ',S1‚äÉSC
       R‚Üê0 ‚ãÑ :Return
     :EndIf
     :If (NAME‚â¢S2‚äÉSC)‚àß~(‚äÇNAME S2)‚àäXBOUND
       ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: ',NAME,' line ',(‚çïJ),' star ',(‚çïS2),' (',(S2‚äÉSTARNAMES),') belongs to ',S2‚äÉSC
       R‚Üê0 ‚ãÑ :Return
     :EndIf
   :EndFor
 :EndFor

‚çù --- No duplicate constellation names ---
 ALLNAMES‚Üê{1‚äÉ‚çµ}¬®CDATA
 :If (‚â¢ALLNAMES)‚âÝ‚â¢‚à™ALLNAMES
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: duplicate constellation names found'
   R‚Üê0 ‚ãÑ :Return
 :EndIf

‚çù --- Constellation name must appear in STARCONSTELLATION ---
 :For I :In ‚ç≥‚â¢ALLNAMES
   :If ~(‚äÇI‚äÉALLNAMES)‚àäSC
     ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: constellation ',(I‚äÉALLNAMES),' not found in STARCONSTELLATION'
     R‚Üê0
   :EndIf
 :EndFor

‚çù --- Spot checks: well-known constellations must be present ---
 :If ~(‚äÇ'Ori')‚àäALLNAMES
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: Orion missing'
   R‚Üê0
 :EndIf
 :If ~(‚äÇ'UMa')‚àäALLNAMES
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: Ursa Major missing'
   R‚Üê0
 :EndIf
 :If ~(‚äÇ'Cas')‚àäALLNAMES
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: Cassiopeia missing'
   R‚Üê0
 :EndIf
 :If ~(‚äÇ'Cyg')‚àäALLNAMES
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: Cygnus missing'
   R‚Üê0
 :EndIf
 :If ~(‚äÇ'Sco')‚àäALLNAMES
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: Scorpius missing'
   R‚Üê0
 :EndIf
 :If ~(‚äÇ'Cru')‚àäALLNAMES
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: Crux missing'
   R‚Üê0
 :EndIf

‚çù --- Orion belt: delta-epsilon-zeta (220-221-222) connected ---
 C‚ÜêCDATA‚äÉ‚ç®ALLNAMES‚ç≥‚äÇ'Ori'
 LINES‚Üê2‚äÉC
 :If ~(‚à®/((LINES[;1]=220)‚àßLINES[;2]=221)‚à®(LINES[;1]=221)‚àßLINES[;2]=220)
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: Orion missing delta-epsilon belt segment'
   R‚Üê0
 :EndIf
 :If ~(‚à®/((LINES[;1]=221)‚àßLINES[;2]=222)‚à®(LINES[;1]=222)‚àßLINES[;2]=221)
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: Orion missing epsilon-zeta belt segment'
   R‚Üê0
 :EndIf

‚çù --- Big Dipper: Dubhe-Merak (300-301) connected ---
 C‚ÜêCDATA‚äÉ‚ç®ALLNAMES‚ç≥‚äÇ'UMa'
 LINES‚Üê2‚äÉC
 :If ~(‚à®/((LINES[;1]=300)‚àßLINES[;2]=301)‚à®(LINES[;1]=301)‚àßLINES[;2]=300)
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: UMa missing Dubhe-Merak segment'
   R‚Üê0
 :EndIf

‚çù --- Crux: two crossing axes (97-99, 98-100) ---
 C‚ÜêCDATA‚äÉ‚ç®ALLNAMES‚ç≥‚äÇ'Cru'
 LINES‚Üê2‚äÉC
 :If ~(‚à®/((LINES[;1]=97)‚àßLINES[;2]=99)‚à®(LINES[;1]=99)‚àßLINES[;2]=97)
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: Crux missing alpha-gamma axis'
   R‚Üê0
 :EndIf
 :If ~(‚à®/((LINES[;1]=98)‚àßLINES[;2]=100)‚à®(LINES[;1]=100)‚àßLINES[;2]=98)
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: Crux missing beta-delta axis'
   R‚Üê0
 :EndIf

‚çù --- Cassiopeia W: chain beta-alpha-gamma-delta-epsilon (51-50-52-53-54) ---
 C‚ÜêCDATA‚äÉ‚ç®ALLNAMES‚ç≥‚äÇ'Cas'
 LINES‚Üê2‚äÉC
 :If ~(‚à®/((LINES[;1]=51)‚àßLINES[;2]=50)‚à®(LINES[;1]=50)‚àßLINES[;2]=51)
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: Cas missing Caph-Schedir segment'
   R‚Üê0
 :EndIf
 :If ~(‚à®/((LINES[;1]=52)‚àßLINES[;2]=53)‚à®(LINES[;1]=53)‚àßLINES[;2]=52)
   ‚éï‚Üê'FAIL: Cas missing gamma-Ruchbah segment'
   R‚Üê0
 :EndIf

‚çù --- Summary ---
 NTOTAL‚Üê+/{‚äÉ‚ç¥2‚äÉ‚çµ}¬®CDATA
 :If R
   ‚éï‚Üê'PASS: TEST_CONSTELLATIONS (',(‚çï‚â¢CDATA),' constellations, ',(‚çïNTOTAL),' line segments)'
 :EndIf
